      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Manna Girds irr fafista/ \nun kalftufi ta Sahle/ ta ka eß ar- \nri aifmirtfu mannu Maifi ehft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Manni Kault peelfhp pee \nmannas Meefas zaur Kaufscha- \nnu un Nopuhfchann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Es efinu itt ka Dum- \npis Tuksneti/ es efinu ka Ap- \npohgs eekfh ifpohstitahm Wee- \ntahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Es efinu nomohdā/ un ta \npatt ka weentulis Putnis us \nJuntu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Manni Genaidneeki neewa \nmanni zaur wiffu Deenu/ kas \nprett manni trakfo/ tee swehre \npee manni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Jo es ehmu Pelnus ta \npatt ka Maisi/ un fajanzu tawu \nDsehreenu ar Affarahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Tawas Skummibas un \nDusinibas pehz/ jo tu effi mann \npazehlis/ un atkat nogahsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Mannas Deenas irr ka \nweena nolehkufi Ehna/ un es \nkalttu ta ka Sahle.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Bet tu KUNGS pa- \nleez mubſchtgi/ un tawa Peemin- \nnejchana lihds Raddu Raddeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Tu gribbetu zeltees/ un \npahr Ziann apschehlotees/ jo jaw \nLaiks irr/ ka tew ja-apschehlo- \njahs/ jo tas nospreests Laiks irr \nnahzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Jo tawi Kalvi wehle \nwienas Afmian (Ustaafifcha- \nnu)/ un schehlojahs ka ta Pihsch- \nlös gull.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Ka tee Bagami ta KUN- \nGA Wahrdü bihſtahs/ un wiffi \n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Ka tas KUNGS Zian \nustaifibs/ un parahdiſees eekf \nfawas Gohdibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Wiꞥſch greeschahs pee \nBehdigu Luhgſchanas/ un \nnizzina winnu Peeluhgſchann\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Lai tas tohp uſrakſtib \npreeſch teem Pehznahſkameen \nun tee Landis/ kas radditi tap \nto KUNGU flawebs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Jo wiꞥſch flattahs no \nwas fwiehtas Augſtibas/ t\nKUNGS luhko no Debbes wi \nSemmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Ka wiꞥſch to Zeetumne \nku Nepuhſchanu klaufa/ un a \nſwabbina tohs Nahwes Beh \nnus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Ka ta KUNGA Wahri \ntohp fluddinahts Zianā/ un wi \nna Teikſchana Jerufaleme.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Kad tee Landis fapulz \njahs kohpa/ un tahs Walſtib \ntam KUNGAM kalpoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Wiꞥſch paſemmo us \nZeitu mannu Spehku/ wiſc \npaihtina mannas Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Es jaffu ta: Man \nSTIPRAJS DEEWS \nxemin mannis nobſt mann \nDeenn puſs Mehrā. Tawi Ga \ndi paleek lihds Raddu Raddeen\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Tu effi zittkahrt to Sei \nmi dibbinajs/ un tahs Debbeti \nirr tawu Rohku Darbs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "27. Tahs fuddins/ bet tu pa \nſahweſi/ tahs iſdils wiffas/ \nweena Drehbe/ tu pahrwehrti \ntab\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
